    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a Pytest Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Pytest</application> framework makes it easy to write
small, readable tests, and can scale to support complex functional testing
for applications and libraries.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

